 EnlargeForm←{
 ⍝ Enlarge the form by firing a "Configure" event in order to make the
 ⍝ hit list visible which has originally a height of nn pixels.
     44<n.HitList.Size[0]:⍬
     vals←n.Form.Posn,(n.Form.height[1]+n.HitList.height),n.Form.Size[1]  ⍝ Enlarge the form
     _←2 ⎕NQ n.Form'Configure',vals
     ⍬
 }
